Package com.heslington_hustle.screens

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActivityScreen
    The ActivityScreen class extends the ScreenAdapter class and is displayed if the player wishes to perform a specific activity.
    CharacterSelectionScreen
    This class extends the ScreenAdapter class, representing the screen where the player selects their character.
    EndGameScreen
    This class extends the ScreenAdapter class and represents the end game screen displayed when the player completes the game.
    ErrorScreen
    This class extends the ScreenAdapter class and represents an error screen displayed when the player encounters certain errors during gameplay, such as running out of time or energy.
    GameScreen
    GameScreen extends the ScreenAdapter class, representing the main game screen where the player can freely roam around the map, interact with activities, and manage their character's energy and time.
    HowToPlayScreen
    This class extends the ScreenAdapter class, representing the screen that provides instructions to play the game.
    MainMenuScreen
    The MainMenuScreen extends the ScreenAdapter class and represents the main menu screen of the game.
    NewDayScreen
    NewDayScreen class represents the screen displayed at the beginning of a new day in the game.
    PauseScreen
    PauseScreen extends the ScreenAdapter class and represents the screen displayed when the game is paused.
